Published on Sep 17, 2014
Every year during the Pebble Beach Concours d'Elegance, there is the Tour d'Elegance. Owners can opt to wake up early on Thursday and drive their cars around Monterey, showing off their cars, and proving they can run. In the event of a tie (on Sunday) a car that drove the tour is given the victory over a car that didn't.
